      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds high, but I've seen other NGOs report much lower numbers for overhead. Can you walk me through the specific breakdown? I'm seeing some internal notes from our auditors suggesting that the ratio of field aid to administrative/marketing spend might be closer to 60/40. Is there a reason for that discrepancy?",
